{"tid":2067761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"空置校舍用地77%建議長遠保留作政府機構或社區用途","createTime":"2020-06-17T08:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:41:57.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"98211cbcebc07ee666327f740f63fa2585e8e4d0","tid":2067761,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"空置校舍用地77%建議長遠保留作政府機構或社區用途<br />\n2020-06-17 HKT 15:49<br />\n<br />\n規劃署更新空置校舍用地報告，截至今年3月，署方檢討234幅空置校舍用地的土地用途，當中181幅建議長遠保留作政府、機構或社區用途，比例達77%。另外，約一成即26幅用地建議長遠作住宅用途，當中14幅建議作公營房屋發展，部分已落成或興建。<br />\n<br />\n餘下27幅位於鄉村範圍的前新界村校空置用地，則建議長遠保留作鄉村式發展、鄉郊用途、休憩用途等。<br />\n<br />\n規劃署表示，當個別空置校舍用地的長遠用途未落實以前，相關部門可安排有關用地作政府臨時用途，或可供非政府機構或社會企業申請使用。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532598-20200617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532598-20200617.htm&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=a46b97bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532598-20200617.htm&h=9d24e50a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532598-20200617.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4d993735780ac9eec19287591a55243ef998e10f","tid":2067761,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"用作黨衛軍基地"},{"pid":"01d59c644779b30a27176171e781178209145394","tid":2067761,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"廢事清理就認啦,知道堆田區容納唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46212e00d81c455556903dd5ceb0a461fa52e2b","tid":2067761,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"&quot;約一成即26幅用地建議長遠作住宅用途&quot;<br />\n<br />\n得一成咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee4ba1c680bb511211c8baa47a66d5e34f6d27c","tid":2067761,"uid":3